		"description": "<p>This halberd grants a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with it. Its blades are silvered, and it deals an extra 2d8 radiant damage to fiends and undead.</p>\n<p>Additionally, once per dawn, when you hit with a melee weapon attack you may choose to have your strike produce a brilliant flash of sunlight. Hostile creatures within 15 feet of you must make a DC 16 Constitution saving throw or be blinded until the start of your next turn. Creatures who are weak to the effects of sunlight (such as a vampire) are affected by this as if they were exposed to the sun.</p>",
